&lt;h3&gt;About the Author&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prof. Gerhard Larcher is full Professor for Financial Mathematics and Head of the Institute for Financial Mathematics and Applied Number Theory at the Johannes Kepler University Linz in Austria. He is the spokesperson of the project 'Quasi-Monte Carlo Methods: Theory and Applications', a special research program funded by the Austrian government.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</dc:description>
